n raised up for people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa'id ibn Jubary reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \"Allah Almighty said: You are the best nation brought forth for people\u00a0(3:110). They are those who emigrated with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, from Mecca to Medina.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 3311 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26214,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/04\/17\/forbids-cruelty-slaves-servants\/","url_meta":{"origin":8395,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Maiming: The Prophet prohibits cruelty to slaves","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 17, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: Zinba' Abi Rawh found his servant boy with a servant girl, so he maimed his nose and castrated him. The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, came afterward, and he said, \u201cWho did this to you?\u201d The boy said, \u201cZinba'.\u201d The Prophet summoned Zinba', and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25265,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/11\/care-for-orphans-free-slaves\/","url_meta":{"origin":8395,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Orphans: Care for the orphans, free the slaves","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 11, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Malik ibn Al-Harith reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever embraces an orphan of two Muslim parents by feeding him and giving him drink until he is independent of him, Paradise will certainly be necessary for him. Whoever emancipates a Muslim man, he will\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43710,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/15\/best-ummah-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":8395,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Best of Ummah are Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 15, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: In the lifetime of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while his companions were numerous, we preferred Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman, then we would remain silent. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 4626 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut Imam Ahmad commented, \u201cThe best of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9956,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/24\/martyrdom-prophet-muhammad\/","url_meta":{"origin":8395,"position":4},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Muhammad: Martyrdom of the Messenger of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Ahwas reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cFor me to swear by Allah nine times that the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, had been killed is more beloved to me than swearing once that he was not, for Allah Almighty\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23399,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/07\/05\/madinah-irhab-cursed-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":8395,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Madinah: Whoever terrorizes Medina is cursed by Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 5, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Sa\u2019ib ibn Khallad reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever terrorizes the people of Medina with oppression, Allah will terrorize him. The curse of Allah, the angels, and the people altogether will be upon him. Allah will not accept his obligatory or voluntary good\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8395","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8395"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"h